with Angels expanding patrols; INSERTS 1 graf after 19th graf,
``These guys ...,'' to ADD comment from mayor.</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By BILL STIEG</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
