t Thursday, the <ORGANIZATION> Mercantile </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Exchange </ORGANIZATION> said its board adopted a resolution Wednesday night saying it `` intends to pursue the consolidation of appropriate operational and administrative functions.'' It said consolidation would maximize efficiency and productivity and achieve economies of scale. The <ORGANIZATION> Mercantile </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Exchange </ORGANIZATION>'s board asked committees of both exchanges to `` develop specific plans to consolidate operations'' with the Comex.
